Intro When it comes to UI rendering, there&rsquo;s no one-size-fits-all &ldquo;correct way.&rdquo; This is especially true for us because we&rsquo;re building across various platforms and ecosystems, each with its unique user behavior. Consequently, there&rsquo;s no universal UI rendering approach that suits every situation.
In today&rsquo;s article, we&rsquo;ll delve into our first component: the &ldquo;Neko Profile.&rdquo;
What is an Neko Profile A Neko profile is what we call our &ldquo;user.&rdquo; This term applies not only to Mochi but also to everything we&rsquo;ve built, from Pod Town to NFTs and beyond.

